title: Nature's Pantry
description: Natural foods market offering selections in gluten-free, wheat-free and dairy-free alternatives for those with allergies as well as the usual groceries, vitamins, herbs, books, coffees & teas, pet products, refrigerated foods, locally grown produce. Special orders taken. New location since spring 2010.
